00:17:10,484 --> 00:17:12,369
Vozidlo na dvanástej hodine.

233
00:17:12,820 --> 00:17:14,204
Na jedenástej.

234
00:17:14,697 --> 00:17:15,872
Na desiatej.

235
00:17:18,909 --> 00:17:20,335
A na druhej hodine.

236
00:17:25,666 --> 00:17:28,010
Tri dodávky a sedan.

